px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：定慧</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Claude Code 正式上线语音模式：输入 /voice，长按空格说话，松开即完成输入。语音转录实时流入光标位置，和键盘无缝切换，转录Token完全免费。编程的下一个战场不是模型智商，而是交互方式。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">刚刚，Anthropic给Claude Code加了个语音模式。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"173\" data-backw=\"562\" data-ratio=\"0.30743243243243246\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-w=\"1184\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b3650026&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYUxicD45q9KsDIpxtneibud6fcllmWTUVuGBLvv6HQQwF2bXlEBQFmKLS6kjpgLRianGW9H0AJib4J4Maib4aN4rJUuZJBCZcwbPrkI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"251\" data-backw=\"562\" data-ratio=\"0.44703770197486536\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-w=\"1114\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e0b1e4cd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYU8QXMrtUPwjWv6p6KG4aic37BHQNMM3ZbknszYQ1HTTsfTX47qy9P7ulXPhjgxptPTOlYIoVkicialEoTWKJ4wBEPib2xAfl3ZrtA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">以后写代码，用嘴说就行。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"700\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"562\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6927ad96&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FRvq8Ow69CYU0hhicheAAOicW5jaFDuMX6zZbibmwKq14oNOuOdNuWZX9QL89qXfYHd4DET4StBPPI9hy0xqc533ooPjiceSkRkzHSMzkMygJZac%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code是Anthropic出品的命令行AI编程工具。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">以前你得打字跟它交流。现在不用了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">输入/voice命令，开启语音模式。长按空格键说话，松开完成输入。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">跟对讲机一模一样。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"1\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-w=\"700\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5a90d3d1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FRvq8Ow69CYXpgMBl3m83hTcAPpSnocdIeAnBIg4ERvOvMo8o2gpp1vKpnRW3dVIm6lUcuxiaWS4IzqLkbU4FlzdKmh73veyyLnBguKwZjznE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">目前灰度测试阶段，大约5%的用户先尝鲜，接下来几周逐步放开。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 48px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你的账户有权限，打开Claude Code时欢迎界面会提示你。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">语音模式这玩意儿牛在哪？</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">不是简单的语音转文字。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">语音转出来的文字，会直接在光标位置实时流式输出。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">类似下面网友分享的这样。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mma4rncd18aj\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"700\" data-backw=\"322\" data-ratio=\"2.1739130434782608\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 57%;flex-basis: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"322\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9cae30b7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FRvq8Ow69CYX4Vxf4svRlzEYJdRmjcDJdZkIFhQiavVCoO720vscnLG1KmfL7PbXZXRELOOxR3peTcz846ndb0EQEVAqKvdibibTGZArTLOhQlU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">啥意思呢？你可以先手打一半提示词，遇到复杂逻辑懒得打字了，长按空格切到语音，吐槽一通那段难以描述的逻辑，松手，再继续打字。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">无缝衔接。不覆盖。不替换。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">这才是关键——它不是替代键盘，是补充键盘。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">想象一个场景：你在调一个诡异的bug，涉及三层回调嵌套加一个竞态条件。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">打字描述这玩意儿，光组织语言就得五分钟。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">但如果张嘴说？人类天生就擅长口头描述混乱的场景。三十秒搞定。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">还有一个大利好：</span><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">语音转录的Token完全免费。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">不计费。不扣额度。想说多少说多少。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0356db0c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb351381bTy5MO2IN89mV41M88GEiaCCibDxJoaQjYV6HfRtafnmEmfM3R1p0tmkHgBOVuXBD6UJKpsQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">对面奥特曼什么反应？</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">有意思的是，OpenAI的Codex几乎在同一时间也加了类似功能。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">Codex 0.105.0版本更新日志写得明明白白——按住空格录音，松开转录，文字直接输入到终端界面。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"392\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"505195746\" data-ratio=\"0.6788874841972187\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1582\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=55741ab1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYX6STKoYNL0comK53aoDMgttWRenCTTJf3IFYZMw8fIYyFKYF0iaKUYh7OkUXLENzVul2lAxx2LjwlQPaQd6urgJ1sdCFTzWVWs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">用的是Wispr语音引擎，目前支持macOS和Windows，Linux还没跟上。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">而且这功能还需要手动开启：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">在配置文件里设置features.voice_transcription=true。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">两家几乎同时出招。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">这不是巧合，是共识。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">编程工具的下一个战场，不在模型有多聪明，而在交互有多自然。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0356db0c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb351381bTy5MO2IN89mV41M88GEiaCCibDxJoaQjYV6HfRtafnmEmfM3R1p0tmkHgBOVuXBD6UJKpsQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">社区怎么看？</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">开发者社区其实早就在自己搞了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">在官方语音模式之前，GitHub上就有一个叫Voice Mode的社区项目，通过MCP协议给Claude Code外挂了语音能力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"313\" data-backw=\"562\" data-ratio=\"0.5560916767189384\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-w=\"1658\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bf23893f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYWsSGlXOo4FW3hcotruIgsSmJXKZ2RNhSVX8w5EJ26OI92yynpRZ2xyb94EmicTIVCwUPiadvvnzdvQZNgLfAv78bBUnWM8MrVMY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">用Whisper做语音识别，用Kokoro做语音合成，甚至能离线跑。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">还有各种第三方工具——AquaVoice、Superwhisper、Voicy——都在抢占语音写代码这个生态位。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"255\" data-backw=\"562\" data-ratio=\"0.45347928068803756\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-w=\"2558\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.de